title: #304: My Daughter Sucks At Suicide (JMScomedy))
itunes:title: My Daughter Sucks At Suicide with Jessica Michelle SIngleton
description: Jessica Michelle Singleton met me in LA to talk about her suicide attempt. It's waaaaay funnier than that. I love hearing about suicide and we did this without any crazy gravity to the subject. Just a good fun talk about ending it all.
